lead_paragraph: West Indies players will be thrown off the squad for the World Twenty20 if they do not agree to financial terms by Sunday's deadline, the head of the region's cricket board said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Windies Board Rejects Call for New Deal in World T20 Row
